      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait sorry i didnt mean to make it sound complicated. i just wanted to know about the science part. what exactly is happening at a microscopic level with the yeast and the bacteria? like how do they interact to make the bread rise?",
      "source": "evaluator",
      "targeted_response_start": "",
